10 E. A municipality or county shall issue the certificates
11 required by paragraphs 2 and 3 of subsection B of this section
12 within ten (10) days after all final inspections are completed.
13 Thereafter if a licensee fails to maintain compliance with
14 municipal or county zoning ordinances and codes, the mayor or chair
15 of the board of county commissioners or their designee, shall
16 forthwith notify the ABLE Commission in writing setting forth
17 details of the noncompliance.
18 F. Within ten (10) days of the receipt of all information
19 required in subsections B through E of this section, ABLE shall
20 notify the applicant in writing of any deficiencies in the
